{"tid":2132910,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中聯辦：堅決支持DQ決定　豈容無良之輩登堂入室?","createTime":"2020-07-30T16:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T23:20:45.000Z","uid":219007,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"56d044d71040a0a893bcf041f220a8ae4bbf3fee","tid":2132910,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T16:10:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20200730-1220copy_IhPKR_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20200730-1220copy_IhPKR_1200x0.png&h=e9ede3f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府選舉主任大規模撤銷（DQ）多人的參選立法會的資格，目前已有 12 名立法會參選人被裁定提名無效。中聯辦同日發聲明，對選舉主任的決定表示堅決支持，指是嚴格根據基本法、香港國安法和香港選舉法律辦事，理據充足，合法合規。<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦質疑，有關人士為癱瘓特區政府、顛覆國家政權、全面「攬炒」香港而來，「怎麼可能真誠擁護基本法和效忠國家、效忠香港特別行政區？承擔重要憲制責任的香港特別行政區立法機關，豈容這些圖謀毀掉『一國兩制』、毀掉香港繁榮穩定的無良之輩登堂入室？」<br />\n<br />\n發言人指出無規矩不成方圓，參選人必須真心實意地擁護《基本法》，效忠香港特別行政區，「我們看到，這些被決定提名無效的人士，其言行均突破了法律底線：有人公開鼓吹『港獨』『自決』；有人『告洋狀』乞求外部勢力制裁香港，干預香港特區事務」。發言人又指，有參選人宣稱當選後將無差別地否決財政預算案和政府法案，以癱瘓特區政府；有人從根本上反對香港國安法，聲稱要「繼續抗爭到底」等，形容他們是「劣跡斑斑」。<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦指前中國領導人鄧小平早就指出「港人治港」有界線和標準，必須由以愛國者為主體的港人來治理香港。中聯辦重申，真誠擁護《基本法》、效忠香港，是對香港從政者的基本政治要求，也是理應遵從的政治倫理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/瘋狂-dq-中聯辦-堅決支持選舉主任決定-豈容無良之輩登堂入室/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%98%8B%E7%8B%82-dq-%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6-%E5%A0%85%E6%B1%BA%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A-%E8%B1%88%E5%AE%B9%E7%84%A1%E8%89%AF%E4%B9%8B%E8%BC%A9%E7%99%BB%E5%A0%82%E5%85%A5%E5%AE%A4%2F&d=PqSGdtEI7oeKzC3efZxDSpq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=e3cecff2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%98%8B%E7%8B%82-dq-%E4%B8%AD%E8%81%AF%E8%BE%A6-%E5%A0%85%E6%B1%BA%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A-%E8%B1%88%E5%AE%B9%E7%84%A1%E8%89%AF%E4%B9%8B%E8%BC%A9%E7%99%BB%E5%A0%82%E5%85%A5%E5%AE%A4%2F&h=e8ac1f9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/瘋狂-dq-中聯辦-堅決支持選舉主任決定-豈容無良之輩登堂入室/</a>"},{"pid":"ba9a281bca8a68419471c82b84a898e920e38a83","tid":2132910,"uid":273703,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T16:16:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b57a3e3d98dc28cfc77c55a0022feb3956bb401","tid":2132910,"uid":325900,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T16:17:19.000Z","msg":"賊喊捉賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34345454b2134d772a6b2acaf1c2f9f8aee3d35f","tid":2132910,"uid":273703,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T16:17:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d26f485e915a3ad103abb1f6c025648f9a964f8a","tid":2132910,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T16:27:04.000Z","msg":"豈容共匪禍國殃民！"},{"pid":"1047538925adf1f71357e981d4ebb316a805194f","tid":2132910,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T17:14:20.000Z","msg":"咁曾經當選而如今被Dq, 使唔使退返薪酬？全部議案重審？"},{"pid":"3c32e4ee579412fb2e274d89387c0fd7f30bc49e","tid":2132910,"uid":71583,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T17:18:22.000Z","msg":"係都由選民用選票DQ<br />\n<br />\n不過呢個唔係民主社會"},{"pid":"5e1bdcba189c8b0c9824b05e4a9b06a481990fd8","tid":2132910,"uid":293624,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T17:20:59.000Z","msg":"仲有幾百萬選民呀，駛唔駛DQ埋個選民資格？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4de15c44c55bc1e64d556c32ce1397d41b662d","tid":2132910,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T19:48:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0c4a8165b36181c377f8fa9fcaf77acb409e07","tid":2132910,"uid":138